Systems stake their Re, a structural score derived from how well a system integrates local identity, interconnection, feedback loops, and evolutionary capacity.

otcomes co-audited by multisig validators, including ecological scientists, local stewards, and AI-driven pattern analysis.
Tokens are minted only when both scores align above defined thresholds. No output without input. No currency without care.
This isn’t just eco-finance. It’s ecological epistemology."

